version_description: The verses are wrong. They should be a C chord to a Csus4 . The chords are also wrong in the Chorus. There is a walkdown that is not detailed in any previous chart. I have provided the TAB to that walkdown that will help readers play the sogn more accurately.
For original key transpose half step down.

I experimented a little bit with the F major 7 chords in the tag so if you'd rather play an F major chord its your call. Also be sure to milk the A minor 7 chords especially when they happen around C major chords 'cause that's an uncommon progression.
The chords are a little simpler than the chords in the recorded version.
